---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Weiyijie Bio">
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About Weiyijie Bio</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Your trusted partner for high-quality natural ingredients, with 10+ years of industry experience serving customers worldwide.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Established in 2014, Weiyijie Bio is a professional supplier of natural ingredients, specializing in plant extracts, cosmetic raw materials, and food additives. Over the past 10 years, we have grown from a small trading company to a comprehensive supplier serving more than 500 customers from 30+ countries around the world.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Our core team has an average of 10+ years of experience in the natural ingredients industry, with deep expertise in product development, quality control, and international trade. We understand the specific needs of different markets and industries, and we are committed to providing our customers with high-quality products and professional services.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">We work closely with a number of GMP certified factories in China, and we have established a strict quality control system to ensure that every batch of products meets international standards and our customers' requirements.</p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">To provide our customers with high-quality natural ingredients at competitive prices, supported by professional technical support and excellent customer service, to help them succeed in their markets.</p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Our Vision</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">To become the leading global supplier of natural ingredients, recognized for our product quality, technical expertise, and customer-centric service.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556740755-069a40165b40?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" 
            alt="Weiyijie Bio Team" 
            class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full h-auto"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 核心优势 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">📊</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">10+ Years Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Core team with deep industry expertise and market understanding</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Global Service</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Serving 500+ customers from 30+ countries across 5 continents</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">🏭</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">GMP Certified Factories</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Strictly selected cooperative factories with complete certifications</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Customer First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">24/7 customer support, flexible MOQ, and customized solutions</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 地址和联系方式 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Contact Information</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">📍</span>
                <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Address:</strong> No. 16, Fengqi West Road, Chang'an District, Xi'an, Shaanxi, China</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">📧</span>
                <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Email:</strong> sales@weiyijiebio.com</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">📱</span>
                <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Phone/WhatsApp/WeChat:</strong> +86 19909215700</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">⏰</span>
                <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 9:00 AM - 18:00 PM (GMT+8), Monday to Friday</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Factory</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Our cooperative factories are located in Shaanxi, China, covering a total area of 20,000 square meters, with modern production equipment and a professional R&D center. The factories have an annual production capacity of 500 tons of plant extracts, 200 tons of cosmetic raw materials, and 300 tons of food additives.</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all">
              Contact Us for Factory Visit
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
